<li><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Motifs" title="Main/Motifs">Motifs</a></li>
<li><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NarrativeDevices" title="Main/NarrativeDevices">Narrative Devices</a></li>
